2018-10-03 18-00-00:
	Title: RAGL Season 6
	Author: netnazgul
	Content: Attention, players! Sign-in period for Season 6 of the Red Alert Global League is closing in just a week's time.\nAgain you have the chance to participate in the biggest tournament in the OpenRA community and compete against other challengers for prizes and glory - this season everyone has the chance to get his hands on a share of the prize pool! Also there is a qualification stage for newcomers to prove your worth and be allowed into the main brackets.\n\nRegistrations close on October 10th, qualifying stage is to be held on October 13th, and the main event runs from October 15th till December 23rd. Check all the information at https://www.openra.net.
